FBIS4-61214 "drsov087_b_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-087 Daily Report 4 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Appoints Social Security Minister Yeltsin Appoints Social Security Minister LD0405144094 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1343 GMT 4 May 94 LD0405144094 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [Text] Moscow, 4 May (ITAR-TASS) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin has signed a decree appointing Lyudmila Bezlepkina as minister of social security of the Russian Federation. Prior to this appointment, Lyudmila Bezlepkina was a first deputy minister of social security of the Russian Federation.
